Heilie CombrinckLiving with diabetes is not easy, but with the right support system and lifestyle you can manage to enjoy your life. This is the message portrayed the past few years at the monthly meetings of the Diabetes Support Group in Uitenhage.On Wednesday, June 1st, podiatrist Stuart Alexander will be talking about the effects of diabetes on your feet and limbs. The meeting will be held at the Andries Marais Boardroom at the Netcare Cuyler Hospital at 18:00.Support group s last meeting: Razya Nathoo from the Diabetes Support Group in Uitenhage said that owing to unforeseen circumstances, this will be the last meeting of the year.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.